Give us the choice to;

A: Leave the EU & be run by parliament.

Or;

B: Stay in the EU. Be governed from Brussels & abolish Parliament.

Either way would save the country a fortune by A: Getting rid of all the MEP's wages & expense accounts & not having to pump money into the black hole that is the EEC... Or B: We'd save 650 Westminster wages & expenses... Plus all those civil servants that wouldn't be needed.
